        <heading>GENERAL PROVISIONS</heading>
        <section eId="sec_28-010">
          <num>28.010</num>
          <heading>Definitions.</heading>
          <content>
            <p>As
used in this title, unless the context otherwise requires, the words and terms
defined inNRS 28.020to28.130, inclusive, have the meanings
ascribed to them in those sections.</p>
