        <section eId="sec_28-140">
          <num>28.140</num>
          <heading>Interpretation.</heading>
          <content>
            <p>As
used in this title, every mode of oral statement, under oath or affirmation, is
embraced by the term ï¿½testify,ï¿½ and every written one by the term ï¿½depose.ï¿½</p>
